#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:4
msgid "lmcache bench engine"
msgstr "lmcache 基准引擎"

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:6
msgid ""
"The ``lmcache bench engine`` command runs sustained performance "
"benchmarks against an inference engine (e.g., vLLM). It supports multiple"
" workload types that exercise different caching patterns and reports "
"TTFT, decoding speed, and throughput metrics."
msgstr "``lmcache bench engine`` 命令对推理引擎（例如 vLLM）进行持续性能基准测试。它支持多种工作负载类型，以测试不同的缓存模式，并报告 TTFT、解码速度和吞吐量指标。"

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:15
msgid "There are three ways to configure the benchmark:"
msgstr "配置基准测试有三种方法："

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:17
msgid "**CLI arguments** -- pass all options on the command line."
msgstr "**CLI 参数** -- 在命令行中传递所有选项。"

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:18
msgid ""
"**Interactive mode** -- run ``lmcache bench engine`` without required "
"args and follow the step-by-step prompts."
msgstr "**交互模式** -- 运行 ``lmcache bench engine`` 而不需要参数，并按照逐步提示进行操作。"

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:20
msgid ""
"**Config file** -- save a configuration to JSON and replay it with "
"``--config``."
msgstr "**配置文件** -- 将配置保存为 JSON 并使用 ``--config`` 进行重放。"

