"entering interactive mode. Useful in automated pipelines."
msgstr "如果缺少任何必需的参数，则立即报错，而不是进入交互模式。这在自动化管道中非常有用。"

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:83
msgid ""
"If you don't have an LMCache server, you can pass ``--tokens-per-gb-"
"kvcache`` directly instead of ``--lmcache-url`` (see :ref:`bench-tokens-"
"per-gb` for how to find this value)."
