msgid "Terminal (real-time progress)"
msgstr "终端（实时进度）"

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:570
msgid ""
"During the benchmark, a live progress display shows in-flight requests, "
"average TTFT, decode speed, and throughput. Suppress it with ``-q``."
msgstr "在基准测试期间，实时进度显示会显示正在进行的请求、平均 TTFT、解码速度和吞吐量。使用 ``-q`` 可以抑制它。"

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:574
