"``bench_summary.json`` -- aggregate statistics with percentiles and "
"config metadata. Opt-in with ``--json``."
msgstr "``bench_summary.json`` -- 聚合统计数据，包括百分位数和配置元数据。通过 ``--json`` 选项启用。"

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:613
